data.description: Hard wood floors throughout the first floor.  Largest driveway in the neighbor hood. Three fireplaces (master bedroom, family room, living area).  Granite counters and lots of cabinets space with an island in the kitchen.  New HVAC, tankless water heater, dishwasher, convection microwave. Upgraded master bath
data.whatILove: With four bedrooms upstairs, a family room, dining area, and living room down stairs, this house has lots of flexibility.  It has the LARGEST driveway in the community and can easily fit 3 cars. It has a nice concrete patio prewired for a hot tub.  Walk out balcony with access from 2 bedrooms. We have some great plans for this house.  Stay tuned.
